Class AgeSearchTree<E extends AgeDataInterface<E>>

java.lang.Object
com.abdcelik.BinaryTree<E>
com.abdcelik.BinarySearchTree<E>
com.abdcelik.AgeSearchTree<E>
Type Parameters:
E - generic type of AgeSearchTree
All Implemented Interfaces:
SearchTree<E>, java.io.Serializable
public class AgeSearchTree<E extends AgeDataInterface<E>>
extends BinarySearchTree<E>
AgeSearchTree class keeps a binary search tree. Generic type should implement AgeDataInterface. Each node has an age and number of people at this age.
